title: #231 - Process Philosophy
itunes:title: #231 - Process Philosophy
description: It's all about the process, baby! At least, it is this week on Drunken Philosophy where a very sleepy Connor and Dan discuss Alfred Whitehead's book 'Process and Reality' as well as the broader ideas behind process philosophy. Get out of here substance! We don't need ya anymore!
